small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionstart_event\"><code>transitionstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcechanged_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcechanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcedown_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforceup_event\"><code>webkitmouseforceup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcewillbegin_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcewillbegin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>wheel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>setAttributeNode</code> dodaje do elementu nowy węzeł typu <code>Attr</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>zastąpionyAtr</i> = element.setAttributeNode(<i>atrybut</i>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>atrybut</code> jest węzłem typu <code>Attr</code></li>\n <li><code>zastąpionyAtr</code> jest węzłem zastąpionego atrybutu - jeśli był taki - zwróconym przez tę metodę</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">// &lt;div id=\"raz\" align=\"left\"&gt;raz&lt;/div&gt;\n// &lt;div id=\"dwa\"&gt;dwa&lt;/div&gt;\nd1 = document.getElementById(\"raz\");\nd2 = document.getElementById(\"dwa\");\na = d1.getAttributeNode(\"align\");\nd2.setAttributeNode(a);\nalert(d2.attributes[1].value)\n// wypisze: \"left\"\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Jeżeli istnieje już atrybut o danej nazwie, zostanie on zastąpiony nowym atrybutem i zwrócony jako wynik funkcji.</p>\n<p>Tej metody używa się rzadko - do zmiany atrybutów elementu zwykle wykorzystywana jest metoda <a href=\"pl/DOM/element.setAttribute\">setAttribute</a>.</p>\n<p></p><p>Metody DOM do obsługi atrybutów to:</p>\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>DOM Level 1 <small>(brak obsługi przestrzeni nazw, najczęściej używane)</small></th>\n<th>DOM Level 2 <small>(obsługa przestrzeni nazw)</small></th>\n<th>DOM Level 1 <small>- praca bezpośrednio z węzłami <code>Attr</code> (rzadko używane)</small></th>\n<th>DOM Level 2 <small>- praca bezpośrednio z węzłami <code>Attr</code>, z obsługą przestrzeni nazw (rzadko używane)</small></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/setAttribute\" title=\"setAttribute\"><code>setAttribute</code></a> (DOM 1)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/setAttributeNS\" title=\"setAttributeNS\"><code>setAttributeNS</code></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/setAttributeNode\" title=\"setAttributeNode\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>setAttributeNode</code></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/setAttributeNodeNS\" title=\"setAttributeNodeNS\"><code>setAttributeNodeNS</code></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/getAttribute\" title=\"getAttribute\"><code>getAttribute</code></a> (DOM 1)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/getAttributeNS\" title=\"getAttributeNS\"><code>getAttributeNS</code></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/getAttributeNode\" title=\"getAttributeNode\"><code>getAttributeNode</code></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/getAttributeNodeNS\" title=\"getAttributeNodeNS\"><code>getAttributeNodeNS</code></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/hasAttribute\" title=\"hasAttribute\"><code>hasAttribute</code></a> (DOM 2)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/hasAttributeNS\" title=\"hasAttributeNS\"><code>hasAttributeNS</code></a></td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/removeAttribute\" title=\"removeAttribute\"><code>removeAttribute</code></a> (DOM 1)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/removeAttributeNS\" title=\"removeAttributeNS\"><code>removeAttributeNS</code></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/removeAttributeNode\" title=\"removeAttributeNode\"><code>removeAttributeNode</code></a></td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-887236154\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: setAttributeNode</a> (wprowadzono w <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#method-setAttributeNode\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core</a></p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"setAttributeNode dodaje do elementu nowy węzeł typu Attr.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element.setAttributeNode()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.setAttributeNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"element.setAttributeNode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Element.setAttributeNode()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/element/setattributenode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/element/setattributenode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/setAttributeNode","title":"element.setAttributeNode"}],"pageTitle":"element.setAttributeNode - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}